      • issueCar

        public boolean issueCar(DriverLicence driverLicence,
                        java.lang.String carType)
        Returns whether the issue operation is success or not. Given a person's driving licence and a specification of the type of car required, determines whether the person is eligible to rent a car of the specified type and issues a car of the specified type.
        参数:

        返回:
